<p t="1015920" d="4800">Crunchy on the outside yeah? It&#39;s 
so interesting, so crunchy, and the  </p>
<p t="1020720" d="10200">combination of sweet and savoury, so delicious. 
I can see why they sell them everywhere here</p>
<p t="1030920" d="17480">Have to be careful with the pips 
though, so many of them. So nice!</p>
<p t="1055080" d="4400">Well, we said earlier it wasn&#39;t that busy, 
it seems like we found the crowds now. This  </p>
<p t="1059480" d="6240">street is full of all sorts of foods, all sorts 
