[Music]</p>
<p t="1093920" d="14400">yeah</p>
<p t="1119040" d="3640">Hello nice to meet you! Hello, 
how are you? Nice to meet you,  </p>
<p t="1122680" d="5680">welcome to Beijing! Thank you very much. We 
are all brothers. What country are you? Uh,  </p>
<p t="1128360" d="8360">England and Russia. Oh England and Russia. 
Yes. We are brothers, we are sisters. Yes,  </p>
<p t="1136720" d="15120">I agree. Welcome to Beijing! Thank you 
thank you. Bye, bye, see you. See you.</p>
<p t="1151840" d="4800">Imagine hearing that all day. Do you 
reckon you just get used to it? We&#39;ve  </p>
<p t="1156640" d="5440">only walked past twice and it&#39;s already done 
my head in. I reckon you just get used to it. </p>
<p t="1162080" d="4360">I don&#39;t know, yeah, maybe it fades out, it&#39;s like 
living under a flight path or something isn&#39;t it.</p>
