<p t="1207120" d="11480">Is it a similar texture to Mochi or not? No 
it&#39;s similar to rice pudding in flavour I think,  </p>
<p t="1218600" d="8440">but it&#39;s a little more bland. Yeah. The 
sweetness comes from the sauce, but itself  </p>
<p t="1227040" d="21502">this thing is not sweet. This thing, in my expert 
