<p t="1248542" d="18">[Music] [Applause]</p>
<p t="1248560" d="4840">So we just got one more snack from the street we 
were just on. We were just walking right towards  </p>
<p t="1253400" d="4480">the exit and then we saw like a group 
of people outside of one of the stores,  </p>
<p t="1257880" d="3040">and they were buying this, which are beef patties  </p>
<p t="1260920" d="10360">with like a pastry that is incredibly 
crispy. And yeah, let&#39;s give it a go!</p>
<p t="1271280" d="8200">Mmm, it&#39;s like a burger, really peppery, 
lots of spices, but wrapped in a pastry.  </p>
<p t="1279480" d="6640">That&#39;s really nice. With the meat inside being 
like a minced meat, the texture is quite soft,  </p>
<p t="1286120" d="4120">but then the pastry on the outside gives it 
a totally different texture. It&#39;s lovely.  </p>
<p t="1290240" d="5960">The crunchy the soft peppery taste, an ever so 
slight spiciness in there, it&#39;s really juicy as  </p>
<p t="1296200" d="20520">well. That&#39;s lovely. Glad we got that. 12 Yuan. So 
that&#39;s about a pound, just over a pound, amazing!</p>
<p t="1316720" d="6040">One thing I wanted to add on to the end of talking 
about that bun, was, it&#39;s really interesting how  </p>
<p t="1322760" d="7360">they have similar types of meat pies and buns 
all the way along what was the former Silk Road. </p>
<p t="1330120" d="4160">And obviously Xian was the end of 
the Silk Road on the Chinese side,  </p>
<p t="1334280" d="6840">or the start of the Silk Road. But yeah it&#39;s 
interesting to see the influence here in Beijing,  </p>
<p t="1341120" d="5680">and the pies are similar to the pies you see 
in Central Asia, in the Caucuses, in Turkiye,  </p>
<p t="1346800" d="13840">and all the way into Europe. I love it we&#39;re so 
far away but also there&#39;s so many similarities.</p>
<p t="1360640" d="7160">What a day, first impressions, as we said a lot 
of times today, of Beijing, are only incredibly,  </p>
<p t="1367800" d="4720">incredibly positive. We&#39;ve had an amazing 
day. We&#39;ve seen some amazing things,  </p>
<p t="1372520" d="3800">tried some amazing things, spoke 
to some incredibly friendly people. </p>
<p t="1376320" d="4520">But uh, time&#39;s getting on, and we have to 
